# Textarea тАФ Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/textarea.css`

## CSS Classes

### Structure
- `.acko-textarea` тАФ flex column, gap `var(--space-2)`
- `.acko-textarea-label` тАФ label-lg typography, `--color-text-default`
- `.acko-textarea-el` тАФ the `<textarea>` element

### Sizing & Resize
- Resize: `none` (hard-coded, no resize handle)
- Min height: `var(--scale-120)` (~120px)
- Max height: `calc(4 * var(--font-body-md-line) + 2 * var(--space-3))` тАФ approx 4 lines
- `overflow-y: auto` тАФ scrolls when content exceeds max-height
- Padding: `var(--space-3) var(--space-4)`
- Font: `--font-body-md-size`, line-height 1.5
- Border radius: `--radius-3xl`

### States (on `.acko-textarea-el`)

| State | Border | Background | Extra |
|-------|--------|-----------|-------|
| Default | `--color-input-border` | `--color-surface` | тАФ |
| Focus (`.acko-textarea-focused`) | `--color-primary` | `--color-surface` | `box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--color-primary)` |
| Error (`.acko-textarea-error`) | `--color-error` | `--color-surface` | тАФ |
| Success (`.acko-textarea-success`) | `--color-success` | `--color-surface` | тАФ |
| Disabled (`.acko-textarea-disabled`) | `--color-border-subtle` | `--color-surface-raised` | `cursor: not-allowed`, `--color-text-disabled` |

### Footer
- `.acko-textarea-footer` тАФ flex justify-between
- `.acko-textarea-helper-text` / `.acko-textarea-error-text` тАФ `--font-caption-size`
- `.acko-textarea-count` тАФ `--font-caption-size`, `--color-text-muted`
- `.acko-textarea-required` тАФ `--color-error`

### Transitions
`border-color 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease`

## React Props
- `resize` prop defaults to `"none"` (only valid value)
- `rows` defaults to 4
- The max-height CSS enforces scrolling regardless of `rows`
